Definition: the power to induce the taking of a course of action or the embracing of a point of view by means of argument or entreaty
Example: the strength of his argument settled the matter
Synonyms: adj, all, persuasive, unpersuasiveness, strength, power, the, to, induce, taking, of, a, course, action, or, embracing, point, view, by, means, argument, entreaty, his, settled, matter
Category: noun.attribute
